## ðŸ’¡ Tips

- **Select code first** before asking questions for better context
- **Keep Zexo AI running** while working on a feature for continuous assistance
- **Use mute** when you need quiet but want to keep context sharing active
- **Combine with Copilot** for the best AI-assisted coding experience

